&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI and LLM platforms, such as ad platform integrations and AI-native distribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data providers covering pre-fill, targeting, predictive, and telematics data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Insurtech ecosystem partners: raters, CRMs, LMS platforms, and agency groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Core insurance platforms such as Guidewire&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Non-traditional demand channels including paid search providers and agency networks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Other partner categories that emerge from market trends or strategic priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
